# Test Scenarios - Login functionality

| Scenario Type  | Test Case Description |
|----------------|-----------------------|
| **Valid Scenarios** | |
| | Validate login with correct username and password |
| | Validate login using Enter key after filling fields |
| | Validate login with trimmed spaces before/after credentials |
| | Validate login with mixed-case username and password |
| | Validate login after modal is reopened (session reset) |
| | Validate modal closes when clicking the "Close" button |
| | Validate password field hides characters (masked input) |
| | Validate login fields accept alphanumeric input |
| | Validate login form accessibility (tab navigation) |
| | Validate login UI renders correctly on mobile devices |
| **Invalid Scenarios** | |
| | Validate login with empty username and password |
| | Validate login with only username filled |
| | Validate login with only password filled |
| | Validate login with incorrect username or password |
| | Validate login with script injection attempt in username/password |
| | Validate login with special characters in fields (e.g., <>[]%) |
| | Validate login with extremely long strings in input fields |
| | Validate login using space-only input |
| | Validate login attempt without internet (if web app) |
| | Validate login after multiple failed attempts (rate-limiting or lockout) |
